hadiths[42]{hadithnumber,text}:
1557,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke daure jahiliyat key logon key liye saal mein do din they jin mein wo kheltey koodtey they. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye to aap ney farmaya : tumharey liye do din they jin main tum khelaa kuda kartey they. ab Allah Taala ney tumhein unkey bajaey do achchhey din dey diye hain. eik eidul-fitr ka din aur eik eidul-azhaa ka din.
1558,"Hazrat Abu Umair bin Anas apney chachaon sey bayan kartey hain ke kuchh logon ney eid ka chaand dekha (magar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bar-waqt ittilaa na mil saki aur aam logon ney roza rakh liya), phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye (aur ittilaa ki) to aap ney logon ko din chadh aaney key baad roza kholney ka aur agley din namaze (eid) key liye nikalney ka hukm diya."
1559,"Hazrat Hafsa (binte Sirin) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr karti thin to mera (baaba) baap aap par fidaa ho jaey, zarur kehti thin. (eik dafa) mainey un sey kaha : kya aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey aisey (yani eidain mein aurton key bahar janey key barey mein) farmatey suna hai? to unhoney kaha : han, (baaba) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baligh aur parda nasheen yahan tak ke haiz wali aurten bhi bahar eid key liye jaeyn aur namaze eid aur musalmanon ki dua mein shareek hon, albatta haiz wali aurten namaz wali jagah sey alag bethi rahen."
1560,"Hazrat Muhammad ( bin Sirin) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey mila aur un sey puchha : kya aap ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (namaze-eid mein aurton ki shirkat key barey mein) kuchh suna hai? aur wo jab bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr karti thin to wo kehti thin : (baaba) mera baap aap par fidaa ho jaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baligh aur parda nasheen aurton ko bhi (eid mein) sath ley kar jao taake wo bhi us neki aur musalmanon ki dua mein shareek hon, albatta haiz wali aurten logon ki namaz wali jagah (eid-gaah) sey alag rahen."
1561,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney bazar mein resham ka eik joda (baraaye farokht) dekha. wo usey ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat aaliya mein hazir huye aur guzarish ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! isey kharid lein aur eid aur wufood sey mulaqat key mawaqe par zebe-tan farmaya karen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye (resham) to un logon ka libas hai jin ka (aakhirat mein) koi hissa nahin. ya (farmaya : ) isey to wo log pehantey hain jinko (aakhirat mein) kuchh nahin milega. kuchh arsa jitna ke Allah Taala ney chaha Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) thehrey rahey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas resham ka eik jubba bheja. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) us jubbey ko ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney to farmaya tha : ye unka libas hai jin ka (aakhirat mein) koi hissa nahin. phir aap ney ye jubba mujhey bhej diya? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey bech kar apni zarooriyaat puri karo."
1562,Hazrat Saulba bin Zahdam sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko (eik dafa) logon par apna naaib muqarrar farmaya. wo eid key din (eid key liye) bahar nikley to farmaya : aey logo ! ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa nahin ke Imam (key namaze-eid padhaaney) sey pehley koi nafl namaz padhi jaaey.
1563,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein  eid ki namaz khutbey sey qabl Azan aur iqaamat key baghair padhaai.
1564,"Hazrat Shaabi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma ney hamein masjid key sutonon mein sey eik sutoon key paas bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein eidul-azhaa key din khutba detey huye farmaya : aaj key din hum sab sey pehley jis chiz ki ibtida (shuruat) kerengey wo ye hai ke hum namaz padhengey, phir (qurbani) zibeh kerengey. jo shakhs aisa kerega, wo hamari sunnat par amal kerega aur jo is (namaz padhney) sey pehley zibeh kerega to ye (qurbani nahin balke) us ney apney ghar walon key liye gosht tayyar kiya hai. ittifaaq se Hazrat Abu-Barda bin Niyar ney (eid ki namaz sey qabl) qurbani zibeh kar di thi. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas eik  nojawan bakra hai jo do daante sey (jismani taur par) behtar hai. aap ney farmaya : chalo usey zibeh kar do lekin aisa janwer terey ilawa kisi sey kifaayat na kerega."
1565,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma eidain mein namaz khutbey sey qabl padha kartey they.
1566,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr aur eidul-azhaa key din chhota neza sath ley jaya kartey they, phir usey gaad letey aur uski taraf namaz padhtey."
1567,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eidul-azhaa ki namaz do rakat hai, eidul-fitr ki namaz do rakat hai, musafir ki namaz do rakat hai aur Jumey ki namaz bhi do rakat hai. ye tamam namazein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani mukammal hain, un mein koi kami aur nuqs nahin."
1568,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) eid key din nikley to aap ney Hazrat Abu Waaqid Laisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us din kon si suraten (namaz eid mein) padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : Sura (Qaaf) aur Sura ( اقتربت الساعۃ ).
1569,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eidain aur Jumey key din Sura (Aala) aur (Ghashiya) padha kartey they. kabhi Juma aur eid eik din mein ikhattey ho jatey to bhi aap yehi dono suraten padhtey.
1570,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain : main gawahi deta hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eid key moqey par hazir huwa. aap ney khutbey sey pehley namaz padhi, phir khutba diya."
1571,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eidey-qurban key din namaz key baad khutba diya.
1572,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eid ki namaz padhaai, phir farmaya : jo aadmi jana chahey wo ja sakta hai aur jo khutba sunney key liye theherna chahta hai, wo thehrey."
1573,Hazrat Abu Ramsaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khutba irshad farmatey suna jabkey aap do sabz (hari) chadaren odhey huye they.
1574,"Hazrat Abu Kaahil Haamisi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, farmatey hain : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko oontni par sawar khutba irshad farmatey dekha jabkey eik habshi (saiyednaa Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) ney oontni ki mahaar (nakel) thaam rakhi thi."
1575,"Hazrat Simaak ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey they? unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey they, phir kuchh der bethtey, phir khadey ho jatey."
1576,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eid ki namaz mein hazir huwa. aap ney baghair Azan aur iqaamat key khutbey sey pehley namaz eid padhaai. jab aap ney namaz puri farmaaee to Bilal key kandhey par haath rakh kar khadey ho gaey. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa ki, logon ko wa'z aur nasihat kartey huye unhein (Allah aur Rasool ki) itaat ki talqin farmaai, phir aap eik taraf sey ho kar aurton ki taraf gaey, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) badastoor aap key sath they. aap ney un (aurton) ko Allah Taala sey darney ka hukm diya aur unhein wa'z aur nasihat farmaai. Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa ki aur unhein Allah (aur Rasool) ki itaat ki raghbat (dichaspi) dilai, phir farmaya : (aey aurton ! ) sadqa karo kyonkey aksar aurten jahannam ka endhan banengi. to eik siyah matyaley rukhsaaron wali aam si aurat ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kyon? aap ney farmaya : tum shikwey shikayat ziyada karti ho aur khawind ki nashukri karti ho. aurten apney haar, baaliyaan aur anguthiyan utaar kar bator sadqa Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key kapdey mein dalney lagin (taake wo baitul-maal mein jama karwa den)."
1577,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr aur eidul-azhaa mein eid gaah tashrif ley jatey aur logon ko namaz padhatey. jab dusri rakat key baad beth kar salam phertey to logon ki taraf munh kar key khadey ho jatey. sab log (apni apni jagahon par) bethey rehtey. agar aap lashkar bhejney ki zarurat mehsus farmatey to logon key samney zikr farmatey warna logon ko sadqa waghera karney ka hukm detey. teen dafa farmatey : sadqa karo. to sadqa karney wali aksar aurten hi hotin.
1578,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tu ney Imam sahab key khutbey key doran mein apney sathi ko zaban sey kaha : chup reh to tu ney bhi fuzul kaam kiya."
1579,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna khutba yun shuru farmatey ke pehley Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan farmatey jo Allah Taala ki shaaney-giraami key laaiq hai, phir farmatey : jisey Allah Taala raahe-raast par ley aaye, usey koi gumrah karney wala nahin aur jisey Allah Taala gumrah kar dey, usey koi raahe-raast par laney wala nahin. bilashuba sab sey ziyada sachchi baat Allah Taala ki kitab hai aur behtareen tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai. aur bad-tareen kaam wo hain jinhein (shariyat mein) apni taraf sey jari kiya gaya. har aisa kaam bid'at hai aur har bid'at gumrahi hai aur har gumrahi aag mein ley jaeygi. phir aap farmatey : mujhey aur qiyamat ko in do ungliyon (angusht shahadat aur sath wali) ki tarah (mila kar) bheja gaya hai. aap jab qiyamat ka zikr farmatey to aap key rukhsaar mubarak surkh ho jatey, aawaz buland ho jati aur ghussey key aasaar chehrey par numaya ho jatey. yun lagta jaisey aap kisi lashkar sey dara rahey hain (yani uskey hamley ki khabar dey rahey hain) ke tum par subah hamla kar deyga ya Sham ko. (phir farmatey : ) jo shakhs maal chhod jaey, wo to uskey rishtey daaron ko milega aur jo aadmi qarz ya chhotey chhotey bachchey (jin key zaya honey ka khatra hai) chhod jaey to wo merey supurd hongey aur unkey ikhrajaat aur qarz waghera ki adaegi merey zimmey hogi kyonkey momineen sey mera talluq aur rishta tamam rishton sey qawi aur mazbut hai."
1580,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eid key din bahar tashrif ley jatey, do rakatein padhtey, phir khutba irshad farmatey aur sadqey ka hukm detey. aksar aurten hi sadqa kartin. agar koi zarurat pesh hoti ya lashkar bhejna maqsud hota to us sey mutalliq kalam farmatey warna wapis tashrif ley aatey."
1581,"Hazrat Hasan Basri sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney Basra mein khutba diya aur farmaya : apney rozon ki Zakat ada karo. log eik dusrey ko dekhney lagey. aap ney farmaya : yahan ehale-Madina mein sey kon log hain? (aey ehale-Madina ! ) utho aur apney (in Basri) bhaiyon ko taalim do (batlao) kyonkey wo nahin jantey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney har chhotey, badey, azad, ghulam aur muzakkir aur muannas par sadqaaey-fitr nisf (aadha) saa gehun ya eik saa khajoor ya jau muqarrar farmaya hai."
1582,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbaaniyon waley din eid ki namaz key baad khutba irshad farmaya, phir farmaya : jis shakhs ney hamari (namaz ki tarah) namaz padhi aur hamari tarah (namaz key baad) qurbani ki, uski qurbani sahih hai, lekin jisney namaz eid sey qabl qurbani zibeh kar di to ye gosht khaney key liye bakri zibeh ki gaee hai (qurbani nahin). Hazrat Abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! mainey to namaz eid key liye aaney sey qabl hi qurbani zibeh kar di hai. mainey socha ke aaj khaney peeney ka din hai, is liye mainey jaldi ki. khud bhi gosht khaya, ehal o ayaal (ghar aur khaandaan walon) aur padausiyon ko bhi khilaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to gosht key liye bakri zibeh ki gaee hai. unhoney kaha : merey paas eik (bakri ki qisam sey) mota taza jazaa hai jo gosht key lihaz sey do bakriyon sey behtar hai (magar wo do daantaa nahin, chhota hai) to kya wo meri taraf sey kifaayat kar jaeyga (agar main usey zibeh kar dun)? aap ney farmaya : han, lekin ye terey ilawa kisi sey kifaayat nahin kerega."
1583,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padha karta tha. aap ki namaz bhi darmiyani hoti thi aur khutba bhi darmiyana hota tha.
1584,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap (pehley) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey phir (thodi der key liye) beth jatey aur us doran mein (koi taqreer ya) baat cheet na kartey, phir khadey ho jatey aur doosra khutba irshad farmatey lihaza jo shakhs tujhey bataey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) beth kar khutba detey they, uski tasdeeq na kar."
1585,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey phir beth jatey, phir khadey ho jatey aur chand aayaat tilawat farmatey aur Allah ki baaten zikr farmatey. aap ka khutba bhi darmiyana hota aur namaz bhi."
1586,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par khutba irshad farma rahey they ke Hasan aur Husain Raziallahu anhum samney aa gaey. unhoney surkh qameesen pehan rakhi thin. wo chaltey they to (qameeson ki wajeh sey) ladkhadaatey they (yani girtey padtey aa rahey they). aap member sey utrey, unhein uthaya aur farmaya : Allah Taala ney sach farmaya hai : ( انما اموالکم واولادکم فتنۃ ),''tumharey maal o aulad tumharey liye aazmaaish hain.''mainey unhein dekha ke apni qameeson mein girtey padtey aa rahey hain to main sabr na kar saka yahan tak ke main member sey utra aur unhein uthaya."
1587,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Aabis sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : kya aap kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eid key liye bahar gaey they? unhoney farmaya : haan aur agar aap sey mujhey qurbat na hoti to main aisey moqey par aap key sath na hota kyonkey wo us waqt bachchey they aap us nishan key paas aaye jo Kasir bin Salat key ghar key paas hai aur wahan namaz padhi, phir khutba irshad farmaya, phir aap aurton key paas tashrif ley gaey. unhein wa'z aur nasihat farmaai aur sadqey ka hukm diya. aurten apney haath apney halaq ki taraf badha kar zewar utaarney lagin aur Hazrat Bilal key kapdey mein dalney lagin."
1588,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eid key din bahar nikley aur do rakaten padhin in (do rakat) sey pehley ya inkey baad koi (nafl) namaz nahin padhi.
1589,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani key din khutba irshad farmaya, phir apney do safed aur siyah rang key mendhon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur unhein zibeh farmaya."
1590,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eid-gaah mein qurbani kiya kartey they.
1591,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Jumey aur eid ki namazon mein Sura (Aalaa) aur (Ghashiyaa) padhtey they. jab Juma aur eid eik din ikhattey ho jatey to phir bhi aap yehi dono suraten padhtey.
1592,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya aap eidain mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hazir huye they? unhoney farmaya : han, aap ney din key aaghaz mein eid ki namaz padhi, phir aap ney Jumey ki rukhsat (chhoot) dey di."
1593,"Hazrat Wahab bin Kaisaan ney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma key daur (khilaafat) main Juma aur eid ikhattey ho gaey to unhoney eid key liye nikalney mein der kar di yahan tak ke din (kafi) ooncha ho gaya, phir wo nikley aur khutba diya aur bahut lamba khutba diya, phir utrey aur eid ki namaz padhaai aur us din logon ko Juma nahin padhaya. ye baat Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey zikr ki gaee to unhoney farmaya : unhoney sunnat par amal kiya."
1594,"Hazrat Aaisha sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (eid key din) unkey paas tashrif ley gaey aur unkey yahan (ghar mein) do bachchiyaan daf baja rahi thin. (aap ney unhein na roka, phir Abu-Bakar dakhil huye to) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein daantaa. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rehney do ! har qom ki eid hoti hai (jis mein wo khel kood bhi letey hain)."
1595,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eid key din habshi aaye aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney khelney lagey. aap ney mujhey bulaya. main (aap ki aut mein khadi ho kar) aap key kandhey key ooper sey unhein kheltey dekhney lagi. main dekhti rahi yahan tak ke main khud hi hat gaee.
1596,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap ney mujhey apni chadar sey chupaya huwa tha aur main habshiyon ko masjid mein kheltey huye dekh rahi thi yahan tak ke main hi uktaa gaee. zara andaza lagao eik nau umr ladki jo khel ki bahut shaukeen ho, kitni der tak khadi dekhti rahi hogi (aap itni der tak uskey liye khadey rahey)."
1597,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein dakhil huye to habshi masjid mein (jangi khel) khel rahey they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein daantaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! rehney do. ye banu Arfada (habshi log) hain (aur jangi khel khailana in ki fitrat mein dakhil hai).
1598,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke (walid mohtaram) Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) merey yahaan tashrif laye to merey paas do bachchiyaan daf baja rahi thin aur (jangi) naghmey ga rahi thin jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kapda odhey letey huye they. (Hazrat abu-Bakar ney unhein jhidkaa to) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney chehrey mubarak sey kapda hataayaa aur farmaya : Abu-Bakar ! inhein rehney do. ye eid key din hain. ye wo din they jin mein haji Mina mein hotey hain. (yani ayyaam tashreeq) aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) in dino Madina Munawra mein they.
